{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_08_02",
  "title": "成宮すず 2話 大好きで大切だから",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――すずが芽衣へ対抗心を燃やすようになって、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days after Suzu started feeling competitive towards Mei",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "新しい衣装のデザインを見せてもらったよ\n可愛くて遊び心があって、すず達によく似合いそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw the designs for the new outfits.\nThey're cute‚ playful‚ and they look like they’ll suit you and Mei well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3539267667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.4666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……可愛くて楽しい素敵な衣装なのですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… They’re cute‚ fun‚ and wonderful outfits…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.2999999999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "新曲の振り付けも順調のようだし\nこの調子なら、本番も期待出来そうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The choreography for the new song seems to be going well too‚\nso I’m looking forward to the actual performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね……\nでも、それは全部芽衣が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true…\nBut‚ that’s all because of Mei…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.2666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……すず？　どうかしたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Suzu? What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、なんでもありません。それよりも\n{user}さんにお願いがあるんですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s nothing. More importantly‚\nI have a favor to ask you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6000021619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.4000021618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "明日は丸一日オフなので\nダンスの自主練をしたいのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have the whole day off tomorrow‚\nso I want to do some dance practice on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8000021619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "朝からスタジオを使いたいので\n鍵を貸していただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d like to use the studio from the morning‚\nso could you lend me the key?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8000021619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.1000021618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "貸すのは構わないが\n休日に朝から自主練なんて随分気合いが入ってるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind lending it to you‚ but you’re pretty\nmotivated to be practicing on your day off‚ from the morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.0666688285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "……新しい振り付けをもっと練習して\n早く完璧に踊れるようになりたいのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I want to practice the new choreography more\nand be able to dance it perfectly as soon as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1000021619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.6333354951
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（熱意があるのは分かるが）\n（今日のすずはなんだか焦っているように見えるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I understand your enthusiasm‚）\n（but you seem a bit anxious today‚ Suzu.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7010061445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。鍵は用意しておくから後で取りに来てくれ\n自主練は芽衣と二人でやるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. I’ll have the key ready‚ so come and get it later.\nAre you practicing with Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8333354952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.4000021618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "それは……私だけです\n私だって、いつも芽衣と一緒にいる訳ではありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually… I’ll be practicing alone.\nI don’t always have to be with Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.526404083,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11795.2803095,
          "startTime": 88.3216843925
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.1666688284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "では、後ほど鍵を取りに伺いますわね\n私はレッスンがあるので、これで失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll come by to get the key later.\nI have a lesson now‚ so I’ll excuse myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6333354952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.2333380383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（一人で自主練するのか？）\n（少し気になるな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s practicing alone?）\n（This is a little worrying…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8333380384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8000047049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 96.8000047049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4、5、6、7、8……\nここでターン……きゃっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One‚ two‚ three‚ four‚ five‚ six‚ seven‚ eight…\nAnd turn here… Whoops!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4666713717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……どうしてもここでミスしてしまいますわ\n芽衣はすぐ踊れるようになったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I keep messing up here.\nMei got it right away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2333380384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに練習してるのに\nどうして私は芽衣のようには出来ないんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m practicing so hard‚\nbut why can’t I do it like Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3637060376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（気になって様子を見に来たが）\n（もしかして朝からずっと踊り続けているのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I came to check on her because I was worried…）\n（But has she been dancing nonstop since this morning?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7333380384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、今は練習するしかありませんわ\n出来るようになるまで休んでる暇なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no choice but to practice for now.\nI can’t afford to rest until I get it right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.300004705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！？\nいつからそこにいたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!?\nHow long have you been there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0000006361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから見ていたが、無理し過ぎだ\n何をそんなに焦っているんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been watching for a while now. You’re pushing yourself.\nWhat are you so anxious about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2000006361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "焦ってなんかいませんわ\n私のことはほっといてくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not anxious!\nJust leave me alone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5666673027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳にはいかないよ\n悩みがあるのなら相談してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t do that.\nIf you’re troubled‚ talk to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8000006361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "朝から踊り続けてお腹も空いてるだろ？\n美味しい物でも食べながら話そう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You must be hungry after dancing all morning‚ right?\nLet’s talk over some good food.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6000006361,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6799.999618300007,
