      "text": "きっと芽衣も同じ気持ちだ。芽衣もすずのことが\n大好きで、とても大事に思っているさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure Mei feels the same. Mei also loves you‚ Suzu‚\nand she treasures you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.6999975844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz032.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も、私のことを……？\nでも、私は芽衣に酷いことを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei does… too?\nBut I said such awful things to her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.7333309177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 350.7666779838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh022.m4a",
      "text": "すず……今日はもう帰って、芽衣とのことを\nもう一度ゆっくり考えてみたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu… Why don’t you go back today\nand think about what happened with Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 355.2000118259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-suz033.m4a",
      "text": "……そう、ですわね。私が今やらなければいけないのは\n一人きりで自主練することではありませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right. What I need to do now\nisn’t to practice alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 363.6000118259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 367.3000113172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
