      "text": "今日は、もう帰ることにしますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll go home now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 367.3000113172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_02-koh023.m4a",
      "text": "それがいい。……あ、それから、芽衣が調子を崩して\nいるようだから、すずからも気にかけてやってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a good idea. …Oh‚ and it seems like Mei isn’t feeling well‚\nso please look after her‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 374.7666784926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
